----
== git-hub

* Dozens of useful commands
* All your GitHub from the terminal
* GitHub V3 API
* Easy to Install

----
== Simple Installation / Upgrade

    git clone git@github.com:ingydotnet/git-hub
    export PATH="$PWD/git-hub:$PATH"

    git hub upgrade

== Traditional Installation / Upgrade

    git clone git@github.com:ingydotnet/git-hub
    cd git-hub
    sudo make install

    man git-hub

    cd git-hub
    git pull
    sudo make install

